  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support design decisions for posterior spinal fixation systems, though the formal intended-use scope is not captured in a structured Context of Use record within this package.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending",
