    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for model risk level 3. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved gradation 2 vs. required gradation 3) is acknowledged and documented. The assessment team determined that the overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended use of the FEA model for ASTM F1717 compression-bending prediction, with the test conditions gap noted as a limitation for future multi-condition validation studies.",
